    "The <b>Platinum Watch</b> is a high-tier <linked>Watch</linked> type. The <linked>Gold Watch</linked> is an alternate to it. When equipped in an accessory slot or simply held in the <linked>inventory</linked>, a clock will appear in the upper-right corner of the playing screen, revealing the in-game time accurate to the last minute. A minute of Terraria game time is equivalent to a second of real-world time. It is required for crafting the <linked>GPS</linked> and <linked>1 Second Timer</linked>."
